ChangeList.Description: Added the **attributes** property to the [accessPackageResource](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageResource?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **resources** relationship to the [accessPackageCatalog](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/accesspackagecatalog?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **resourceRoleScopes** relationship to the [accessPackage](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accesspackage?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **resourceEnvironments** relationship to the [entitlementManagement](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/entitlementmanagement?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **resourceRequests** relationship to the [entitlementManagement](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/entitlementmanagement?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **cleanupScheduledDateTime** property to the [accessPackageSubject](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageSubject?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **questions** relationship to the [accessPackageAssignmentPolicy](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentPolicy?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the `answers` property to the [accessPackageAssignmentRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentRequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the **accessPackageNotificationSettings** property to the [accessPackageAssignmentPolicy](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentPolicy?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **accessPackageNotificationSettings** property to the [accessPackageAssignmentPolicy](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentPolicy?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [additionalAccess](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/accesspackageassignment-additionalaccess?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [accessPackageAssignment](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accesspackageassignment?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **incompatibleAccessPackages** relationship to the [accessPackage](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/accesspackage?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **accessPackagesIncompatibleWith** relationship to the [accessPackage](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/accesspackage?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [Get](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/accesspackageassignment-get?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [accessPackageAssignment](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accesspackageassignment?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [crossCloudAzureActiveDirectoryTarget](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/crosscloudazureactivedirectorytenant?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Use this in Azure AD Entitlement Management connected organizations to refer to an Azure Active Directory tenant in another cloud.
Added the **assignmentRequests** relationship to the [entitlementManagement](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/entitlementManagement?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Updated the API path for managing access package assignment requests from `/identityGovernance/entitlementManagement/accessPackageAssignmentRequests/` which will be retired soon to `/identityGovernance/entitlementManagement/assignmentRequests/`.

Added the [additionalAccess](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/accesspackageassignment-additionalaccess?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [accessPackageAssignment](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accesspackageassignment?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added support for application permission `EntitlementManagement.Read.All` to the read operations of the [unifiedRoleAssignment](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleassignment?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added support for application permission `EntitlementManagement.ReadWrite.All` to the read and write operations of the [unifiedRoleAssignment](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedroleassignment?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added support for application permission `EntitlementManagement.Read.All` to the read operations of the [unifiedRoleDefinition](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedroledefinition?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added support for application permission `EntitlementManagement.ReadWrite.All` to the read operations of the [unifiedRoleDefinition](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedroledefinition?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **assignmentPolicies** relationship to the [accessPackage](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackage?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **assignmentPolicy** relationship to the [accessPackageAssignment](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignment?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **assignmentPolicies** relationship to the [entitlementManagement](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/entitlementManagement?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [accessPackageAssignmentPolicy](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/accesspackageassignmentpolicy?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods for controlling how users receive assignments to access packages in entitlement management.

Added the [approval](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/approval?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Use this method in Azure AD Entitlement Management to retrieve approval objects.

Added the [approvalStage](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/approvalstage?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Use this method in Azure AD Entitlement Management to manage approval stages for an approval object.
Added the **accessPackageAssignmentApprovals** relationship to the [entitlementManagement](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/entitlementmanagement?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the `customExtensionCalloutInstances` property to the [accessPackageAssignment](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignment?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the **customExtensionStageSettings** relationship to the [accessPackageAssignmentPolicy](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentPolicy?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the `customExtensionCalloutInstances` property to the [accessPackageAssignmentRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentRequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the **accessPackageCustomWorkflowExtensions** relationship to the [accessPackageCatalog](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageCatalog?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [resume](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/accessPackageAssignmentRequest-resume?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [accessPackageAssignmentRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentRequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **regexPattern** property to the [accessPackageTextInputQuestion](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageTextInputQuestion?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the `automaticRequestSettings` property to the [accessPackageAssignmentPolicy](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentPolicy?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [moveToCatalog](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/accesspackage-movetocatalog?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [accessPackage](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accesspackage?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the `url` property to the [logicAppTriggerEndpointConfiguration](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/logicAppTriggerEndpointConfiguration?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the `customExtensionCalloutInstances` property to the [accessPackageAssignment](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignment?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **customExtensionStageSettings** relationship to the [accessPackageAssignmentPolicy](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentPolicy?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the `customExtensionCalloutInstances` property to the [accessPackageAssignmentRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentRequest?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **isRequestorJustificationRequired** property to the [accessPackageAssignmentApprovalSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentApprovalSettings?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the **isRequestorJustificationRequired** property to the [accessPackageAssignmentRequestRequirements](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentRequestRequirements?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **refresh** method to the [accessPackageResource](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentRequestRequirements?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **justification** property to the [accessPackageAssignmentRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentRequest?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the `verifiableCredentialRequirementStatus` property to the [accessPackageAssignmentRequestRequirements](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentRequestRequirements?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the `verifiableCredentialSettings` property to the [accessPackageAssignmentPolicy](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentPolicy?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the `verifiedCredentialsData` property to the [accessPackageAssignmentRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAssignmentRequest?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **removeAccessWhenTargetLeavesAllowedTargets** property to the [accessPackageAutomaticRequestSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAutomaticRequestSettings?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource type.

Added the **gracePeriodBeforeAccessRemoval** property to the [accessPackageAutomaticRequestSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageAutomaticRequestSettings?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource type.
Added the **subjectLifecycle** property to the [accessPackageSubject](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageSubject?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **subjects** relationship to the [entitlementManagement](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/entitlementManagement?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Deprecated the [customAccessPackageWorkflowExtension](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/customAccessPackageWorkflowExtension?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type and its associated methods for integrating Azure AD entitlement management and Azure Logic Apps. Use the [accessPackageAssignmentRequestWorkflowExtension](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accesspackageassignmentrequestworkflowextension?view=graph-rest-beta) and [accessPackageAssignmentWorkflowExtension](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accesspackageassignmentworkflowextension?view=graph-rest-beta) resource types and their associated methods instead.

Added the [refresh](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/accesspackageresource-refresh?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [accessPackageResource](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accesspackageresource?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **connectionInfo** property to the [accessPackageResourceEnvironment](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessPackageResourceEnvironment?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the **maximumRetries** property to the [customExtensionClientConfiguration](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/customExtensionClientConfiguration?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
